OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Falthough some misty low cloud possible
OL,9,Fin the east. Cold with a touch of
OL,10,Ffrost in places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FDry and mostly sunny
OL,13,Falthough some patchy low cloud may
OL,14,Flinger along the east coast. Warm
OL,15,Facross the west but cooler in the east
OL,16,Fwith an onshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
